Name: Liv
Text: According to the map, we've landed at the designated location—

Name: Liv
Text: The data analysis cabin on space station.

Name: Liv
Text: But... our aircraft has been destroyed...

Name: Lucia
Text: If we can destroy the space station's defense system, we're able to retreat when the main forces arrive.

Name: Lee
Text: These terminals seem bizarre...

Name: Lee
Text: Those are what the report said—the corruption occurred on this space station only.

Name: Lucia
Text: You must be careful, Lee.

Name: Lee
Text: That's...!

Name: Lee
Text: More authorities unlocked...

Name: Lucia
Text: Wait, that cross is guarding the gate...

Name: Liv
Text: According to my preliminary scan result, this type of enemy doesn't have a typical mechanical structure inside its body...

Name: Liv
Text: It is... composed entirely of Punishing Virus...

Name: Lee
Text: This space station must be hiding some important secrets...

Name: Lee
Text: It seems we can do more than just destroying it.

Name: Liv
Text: Guys, I've turned off the space station's remote sensing system.

Name: Lee
Text: Well done, Liv.

Name: Lee
Text: It should be able to reduce its attacks against Babylonia.

Name: Lucia
Text: Yep, this is the first step for us.

Name: Lamia
Text: It's a theme park in the water...

Name: Lamia
Text: Obtain the first Sea Fairy here.

Name: Lamia
Text: The first battle is going to take place here.

Name: Lamia
Text: Explore the next scene.

Name: Lamia
Text: A handle of some trap. Something seems to be missing here.

Name: Lamia
Text: The iron gate is closed. There's a round groove on it.

Name: Lamia
Text: Please image that Lamia is going into the water next.
It seems you can't use it here.
Obtained: <color=#7FFF00>Wooden Pony</color>
Obtained: <color=#7FFF00>Door Disk (Right)</color>
Obtained: <color=#7FFF00>Door Disk (Left)</color>

Name: <color=#00FFFF>Electronic Voice</color>
Text: We're in the underwater protection mode. Would you like to start the drainage program?

Name: Lamia
Text: There should be some useful information over there.

Name: Lamia
Text: So much for the investigation. Let get out of here by the way we came.

Name: Lamia
Text: Looks like we need a bit of manual manipulation here.

Name: Lamia
Text: Now it's acting in a funny way after being soaked.

Name: Lamia
Text: Now there's no water. Look around and see if there's any useful information.

Name: <color=#00FFFF>Electronic Voice</color>
Text: Underwater protection removed. Gate back to normal.

Name: Lamia
Text: The sky... is the sea?

Name: Lamia
Text: Is there really nothing wrong here?

Name: Lamia
Text: Eek! That little thing is leading me to the enemies! Is it the defense system of this place?

Name: Lamia
Text: Seems like someone used to live around here...
Is this a letter?

Name: Lamia
Text: A handle. Something seems to be missing...

Name: Lamia
Text: The gate won't open. There's a round groove on it.

Name: Lamia
Text: A little horse floating on the Red Tide?
Would this wooden horse have something to do with that handle?
Another letter.
It's not meant to be used here.
Alright, new area opened.
A game room? Hate it...
Half of an iron disk. The other half seems to be missing.
There used to be a lot of people here, I guess.
Half of an iron disk. Should be able to open that gate with another half.

Name: Lamia
Text: This place looks more and more like a virtual reality game hall... Did Lithos provide these things for people for entertainment?

Name: Lamia
Text: Wait, that's...

Name: Lamia
Text: Water everywhere... Is this also one of Lithos' defense measures? It seems that he has regained control over this place.

Name: Lamia
Text: Only I can get through. Keep moving onward.

Name: <color=#00FFFF>Electronic Voice</color>
Text: Activate the forced drainage system?

Name: Lamia
Text: Alright. You can come over now.

Name: Lamia
Text: A-anyway, I should see if there's anything useful.

Name: Lamia
Text: Access control should be back to normal now, right?

Name: Lamia
Text: What a hassle...

Name: Lamia
Text: Cthylla's children are here as well? Oh, it's just some test subjects...

Name: Lamia
Text: I should be able to find some information there.

Name: Lamia
Text: Some archived news reports? I'll gather them all for now. I should leave the way I came.

Name: Lamia
Text: A tricky puzzle again... Are those working for Vonnegut all into this kind of stuff?

Name: Lamia
Text: Lithos... I don't want to kill you.

Name: Lithos
Text: We don't have a choice.

Name: Lithos
Text: Let me struggle bitterly until the end.

Name: Image of Arrogance
Text: Looking for truth? I see...

Name: Image of Arrogance
Text: But will you really find what you are looking for behind this door?

Name: Image of Arrogance
Text: Oops, sorry. I talked too much again.

Name: Image of Arrogance
Text: Then again, what difference does it make to a walking corpse like you?

Name: Image of Arrogance
Text: Don't underestimate me, challenger.

Name: Image of Arrogance
Text: Is this the price of arrogance...?

Name: Jetavie
Text: Is this the gate to the center?

Name: Image of Wisdom
Text: You are like an injured beast...

Name: Image of Wisdom
Text: All that killing intent is just a desperate attempt to hide your fear.

Name: Jetavie Beta
Text: What, is your fear making you uncomfortable?

Name: Jetavie Beta
Text: You are nothing but a pathetic coward.

Name: Image of Wisdom
Text: How much of this vast wisdom can you truly grasp?!

Name: Image of Wisdom
Text: The only thing I know is that I know nothing...

Name: Image of Desire
Text: Those who are numb to fear will be the first to die.

Name: Jetavie Beta
Text: Image of Desire, you talk too much.

Name: Image of Desire
Text: Talking to your enemy—you are lonely, aren't you?

Name: Jetavie Beta
Text: How about we fight till death instead of hugging each other?

Name: Image of Desire
Text: Hey, can you still move?

Name: Image of Desire
Text: Good. It would be too boring if you collapse so early. Let's keep going!

Name: Image of Desire
Text: After all... No matter how many times I tried, I'm still no match for you.

Name: Image of Desire
Text: Oh little cutie, can you tell which side is which?

Name: Image of Desire
Text: The real one is here, little fool.

Name: Image of Love & Hatred
Text: Those who dare to ignore love must be corrected.

Name: Image of Love & Hatred
Text: You will hate me, love me.

Name: Image of Love & Hatred
Text: Then become my puppet.

Name: Jetavie
Text: I have no idea what you're talking about...
Is my love not enough?
Just give me your heart!

Name: Image of Love & Hatred
Text: Don't leave me... Why can't you understand love?

Name: Image of Love & Hatred
Text: How is that little one better than me?

Name: Jetavie
Text: Who are you calling little?!
I'll pay you back twofold... no, fourfold!

Name: Sword of the Brave
Text: I only need my left hand to defeat you.

Name: Moth
Text: You will end up just like their corpses...

Name: Sisyphus
Text: Useless! All your efforts will be in vain!

Name: Sister
Text: Your blood will be my paint. Your flesh and bones will be my altar!
As a warrior of Satan, you're incredibly powerful, but you have betrayed the Abyss Cult!

Name: Enemy
Text: Roarrrr!

Name: Girl Chess Player
Text: I'll beat you until you want to play with me!

Name: Gate Keeper
Text: Outsider! Don't even think about causing trouble under my watch!
